org.cornutum.tcases.openapi

Class TcasesOpenApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.TcasesOpenApi

  • public final class TcasesOpenApi
extends Object
    Defines methods for converting between OpenAPI models and Tcases models.

    OpenAPI models must conform to OAS version 3. See https://swagger.io/specification/#specification.
